<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failure Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f4f7fa; 
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 40px auto; 
            background: #ffffff; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4d4d 0%, #d32f2f 100%);
            color: #ffffff; 
            padding: 30px 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content { 
            padding: 30px 25px; 
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .plan-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff4d4d;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .plan-details h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            color: #666666;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .reason-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .reason-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .reason-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px !important;
        }
        .action-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important; 
            padding: 14px 32px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .help-text {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .help-text p {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #0d47a1;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .help-text p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .footer { 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 25px 20px; 
            font-size: 13px; 
            color: #888888;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px 10px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .detail-value {
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⚠️ Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Dear {{default userName "Valued Customer"}},</p>
            
            <p>We're writing to inform you that your recent payment attempt was unsuccessful.</p>

            <div class="plan-details">
                <h3>Payment Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Plan:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{default planName "Subscription Plan"}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Amount:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{amount}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if attemptDate}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Attempt Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{formatDate attemptDate}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            {{#if failureReason}}
            <div class="reason-box">
                <p class="reason-title">Failure Reason:</p>
                <p>{{failureReason}}</p>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="reason-box">
                <p class="reason-title">Possible Reasons:</p>
                <p>This could be due to insufficient funds, an expired card, incorrect payment details, or a temporary issue with your payment provider.</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="help-text">
                <p><strong>What you can do:</strong></p>
                <p>• Verify your payment method has sufficient funds</p>
                <p>• Check that your card details are up to date</p>
                <p>• Ensure your card hasn't expired</p>
                <p>• Contact your bank if the issue persists</p>
            </div>

            <div class="action-section">
                <a href="{{default updatePaymentUrl "https://atsfitt.com/billing"}}" class="button">
                    Update Payment Method
                </a>
            </div>

            <p>If you continue to experience issues or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{default supportEmail "support@atsfitt.com"}}" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">{{default supportEmail "support@atsfitt.com"}}</a>.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Thank you for your understanding.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 5px; color: #666666;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The ATS Fit Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{default year 2025}} ATS Fit. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{default websiteUrl "https://atsfitt.com"}}">Visit our website</a> | 
                <a href="{{default privacyUrl "https://atsfitt.com/privacy"}}">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="{{default termsUrl "https://atsfitt.com/terms"}}">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>